    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<i>这是比利鬼屋的恶作剧之夜，主人为所有可怕的客人准备了相当大的挑战！参加一场别出心裁的捉迷藏比赛：你不知道自己是谁，唯一可以躲藏的地方就是人群中。你能在怪物的海洋中找到自己并证明你是最狡猾、最有洞察力的玩家吗？</i><br><br><strong>主要特点</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>直观的多人游戏</strong>：进入一个易于学习但难以上手的游戏世界掌握捉迷藏的体验，其中发现自己的身份与发现对手一样重要。</li><li><strong>多样化的游戏模式</strong>：无论您喜欢团队还是团队，都可以享受多种游戏模式基于或竞争性的挑战，每个挑战都有自己的一套角色和目标。</li><li><strong>灵活的游戏选项</strong>：本地或在线与 2 至 8 名玩家一起玩，无论您是举办派对还是参加派对，都可以提供无尽的乐趣。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/57be7888fa05a629d36c90d8a92f1a8e.avif?t=1771532201\" width=615 height=153 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/3a740100e6abeb72caa84466a62d1b68.poster.avif?t=1771532201\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/3a740100e6abeb72caa84466a62d1b68.webm?t=1771532201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/3a740100e6abeb72caa84466a62d1b68.mp4?t=1771532201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>谨慎弄清楚你是谁，完成你的目标，并寻找其他玩家——同时保持本色并避免被发现。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/99998eaabf003bd4f6287e867b45eb89.avif?t=1771532201\" width=615 height=153 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/89341477a584970d900707d7320d6231.poster.avif?t=1771532201\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/89341477a584970d900707d7320d6231.webm?t=1771532201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/89341477a584970d900707d7320d6231.mp4?t=1771532201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个游戏模式引入了具有特定目标的不同角色。争取最高分，并在展示每位玩家表现的游戏终局排行榜上赢得炫耀的权利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/02e5fce48d659123c54dc1caba163df4.avif?t=1771532201\" width=615 height=153 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/69bc6fc67bf648660f5b8407d2c90d84.poster.avif?t=1771532201\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/69bc6fc67bf648660f5b8407d2c90d84.webm?t=1771532201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228710/extras/69bc6fc67bf648660f5b8407d2c90d84.mp4?t=1771532201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Where is Billy?</i> 适合 2 到 8 名玩家，本地或在线均可。轻松连接到其他大厅或打开自己的大厅来充实聚会并通过配对系统保持乐趣。",
